column2: b'Pinky Monkey x FaFa Collaboration Animation: At Afternoon of Sunny Day'

b'A collaboration anime between Frente International\'s Pinky candy mascot and Nissan Soap\'s Fafa laundry mascot.\n\nNorth American viewers may recognize Fafa under a different name "Snuggle". The mascot for the fabric softener brand owned by Sun Products.'
